## <a id="uaa"></a> UAA Documentation

<%= vars.ops_manager %> uses User Account and Authentication (UAA) to manage account roles and permissions in <%= vars.ops_manager %> runtimes.

UAA supports access control as OAuth2 services and can store user information internally, or connect to external user stores through LDAP or SAML.

These topics provide general information about UAA:

